is-Grayling.html | location=London | work=The Daily Telegraph | first=Tim | last=Ross | title=People who post 'revenge porn' on internet face two years in jail, says Chris Grayling | trans_title=在网络上发布“复仇色情”的人面临两年的监禁，克里斯·格雷林说 | date=2014-10-12 | accessdate=2016-12-31 | archive-date=2020-01-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200105150232/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/internet/11156239/People-who-post-revenge-porn-on-internet-face-two-years-in-jail-says-Chris-Grayling.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>2014年10月，格雷林向[[英国保守党|保守党]]提出<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.conservatives.com/~/media/Files/Downloadable%20Files/HUMAN_RIGHTS.pdf |format=PDF |title=Protecting Human Rights in the UK |trans_title=保护英国人权 |website=Conservatives.com |accessdate=2016-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116192608/https://www.conservatives.com/~/media/files/downloadable%20Files/human_rights.pdf |archive-date=2016-11-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>了改革人权的建议，以遏制[[欧洲人权法院|欧洲人权法院]]对英国法院裁决的影响，同时尊重英国原来的权利和责任法案中的“[[國際人權文書|國際人權文書]]”。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-29466113 | work=BBC News | title=European human rights rulings 'to be curbed' by Tories | trans_title=欧洲人权裁决被保守党遏制 | date=2014-10-03 | accessdate=2016-12-31 | archive-date=2020-11-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111223940/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-29466113 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/interactive/2014/oct/03/conservatives-human-rights-act-full-document|title=Conservatives plan to scrap Human Rights Act – read the full document|trans_title=保守主义计划废除“人权法” - 阅读完整的文件|work=the Guardian|accessdate=2016-12-31|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108114916/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/interactive/2014/oct/03/conservatives-human-rights-act-full-document|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.itv.com/news/2014-10-03/tories-threaten-to-scrap-human-rights-act-and-replace-it-